# LapseIQ client .dockerignore — Sprint 5 (B2)
#
# Applies when building the client image (build context = ./client).
# The image runs `npm run preview` which serves the prebuilt dist/.
# We KEEP src/ and the Vite config because the build happens inside
# the image — see client/Dockerfile.

# ── Secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.production
.env.*.local

# ── Build artefacts and deps ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# node_modules excluded (npm ci runs inside the image when building locally,
# but for the CI release path, the dist/ is pre-built on the GHA runner and
# this Dockerfile is now a static-serve stage — see Dockerfile.prod header).
node_modules/
.cache/
.vite/
# NOTE 2026-05-12 (v0.5.3): dist/ is NO LONGER excluded. Dockerfile.prod
# now copies a pre-built dist/ from the build context (produced by the GHA
# pre-build step). Without this, the COPY would fail with "no such file."
# For local builds, run `npm run build` first to produce client/dist/.

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# ── Source control / IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Tests and docs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.test.js*
*.spec.js*
__tests__/
test/
tests/
# NOTE 2026-05-12 (v0.5.2): the previous `*.md` blanket exclude was removed
# because `src/legal/*.md` is imported by 5 legal page components via Vite's
# `?raw` query (DemoSandboxNoticePage, EulaPage, SubProcessorsPage,
# PrivacyPage, TermsPage). Excluding them broke the production build in
# subtle ways. Keep markdown files in the build context.

# ── Don't recursively bundle Docker artefacts ────────────────────────────────
Dockerfile
Dockerfile.*
.dockerignore
